<plot>Would you accept a drink when offered? Noel Parker is made such an offer in a place he's never been before In the middle of nowhere in a bar where everyone's his friend Or are they? They seem to know what he thinks, understand what he feels. And just at a point he thinks he can walk away. Noel has to make the decision of his life. Do you know what your soul desires? At the halfway house what would you choose?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?227679</url></doc>
